title: Radio Row interviews with Russell Wilson, Kyle Rudolph, McCourty Twins & More (Football 1/31)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech interview a collection of guests from Radio Row on South Beach. The guys chatted with Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson (:55), NFL draft prospect Jake Fromm (9:00), Vikings tight end Kyle Rudolph (16:00), Patriots teammates and twins Devin and Jason McCourty (29:45), Hall of Famer John Randle (39:00) and actor Carl McDowell (47:15).
